"""Forge consensus engine package (TRD-2).

Implements multi-provider LLM consensus with Claude arbitration.
Parallel generation from two providers, deterministic merge resolution,
and fail-closed behavior on provider disagreement beyond thresholds.

Security assumptions:
    - LLM provider credentials are never stored in this package; they are
      retrieved from the Keychain via the Swift shell's XPC interface.
    - All provider responses are treated as untrusted external input.

Failure behavior:
    - Provider failures fail closed -- no fallback to single-provider mode
      without explicit operator approval.
"""

