Orchestrates the multi-stage build pipeline: scope decomposition, PR
sequencing, code generation, review cycles, CI execution, and gated merges.

Security assumptions:
    - Pipeline stages never execute generated code -- generation and execution
      are strictly separated.
    - All stage transitions are logged and auditable.

Failure behavior:
    - Stage failures halt the pipeline; no automatic stage skipping.
    - Operator gates wait indefinitely -- no auto-approve.
"""

